                    <div class="reveal w-full lg:w-1/2">
                        <h2 class="font-heading text-brand-green font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-xs sm:text-sm mb-2">Who We Are</h2>
                        <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-brand-dark mb-4 sm:mb-6">Solving the UK's Leaking Gutter Problem</h3>
                        
                        <div class="space-y-4 sm:space-y-5 text-gray-600 text-sm sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">
                            <p>
                                Traditional plastic gutters are manufactured in standard lengths. To span the length of a typical home, they must be clipped together. Over time, UV exposure, freezing winters, and heavy rainfall cause these plastic joints to expand, contract, and eventually perish. <strong class="text-brand-dark font-semibold">The result? Unsightly, damaging leaks.</strong>
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                We founded Lancashire Aluminium Seamless Guttering with a simple philosophy: <strong class="text-brand-green">No Joins = No Leaks.</strong>
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                By investing in state-of-the-art mobile extrusion machinery, we eliminate the need for joints entirely. We bring our workshop directly to your driveway, rolling out a continuous, perfectly tailored length of premium aluminium that spans your entire roofline in one seamless piece.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
