                        <h4 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold text-brand-green mb-2">How long does seamless aluminium guttering last?</h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed">
                            Aluminium is highly resistant to corrosion. Under normal UK weather conditions, a seamless aluminium gutter system can easily last upwards of 30 years with minimal maintenance, vastly outperforming standard uPVC.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="reveal reveal-delay-100 bg-brand-dark rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-700">
                        <h4 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold text-brand-green mb-2">Do you cover my area?</h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed">
                            Yes, if you are in the Lancashire or North Yorkshire border region! We are based in Colne and regularly complete installations in Skipton, Burnley, Barrowford, Earby, Keighley, and the surrounding villages.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="reveal reveal-delay-200 bg-brand-dark rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-700">
                        <h4 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold text-brand-green mb-2">What is the "Cut & Drop" service?</h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed">
                            If you are a builder, roofer, or a competent DIYer, we offer a supply-only service. We will bring our machine to your site and extrude the exact lengths of continuous guttering you require, leaving you to handle the installation.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="reveal reveal-delay-300 bg-brand-dark rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-700">
                        <h4 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold text-brand-green mb-2">Can you replace fascias and soffits as well?</h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed">
                            Absolutely. We provide complete roofline replacements. Removing rotten timber fascias and replacing them with solid, maintenance-free materials provides the perfect foundation for your new seamless guttering.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
